    <string name="vision_goal_text">To transform our village into a fully digital, self-sustainable and environmentally friendly smart village while preserving our cultural heritage.</string>
    <string name="facilities_list">• Digital Service Center\n• Public Library\n• Smart Water Supply\n• 24x7 Electricity\n• Community Hall\n• Health Center</string>
